description: Delete a hub content reference in order to remove a model from a private hub.

parameters.name: HubName
parameters.description: The name of the hub to delete the hub content reference from.

parameters.name: HubContentType
parameters.description: The type of hub content reference to delete. The only supported type of hub content reference to delete is ModelReference.

parameters.name: HubContentName
parameters.description: The name of the hub content to delete.
